.com%2Fmedia%2FFprnU4nX0AEcXfe.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"tweet-photo\"></picture></div></div></div></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1628868572653953025\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"tweet-link-bottom\"><div class=\"tweet-footer\"><span class=\"tweet-date\">9:25 PM ‚àô Feb 23, 2023</span><hr><div class=\"tweet-ufi\"><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1628868572653953025/likes\" class=\"likes\"><span class=\"like-count\">312</span><span>Likes</span></span><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1628868572653953025/retweets\" class=\"retweets\"><span class=\"rt-count\">55</span><span>Retweets</span></span></div></div></a></div><p><em>A look at some more monsters we have designed.</em></p><div data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1624108968686518285&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;You have $11 to build a team of tamed monsters.\\n\\nWho you picking? üëÄ &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;TheTreeverse&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Treeverse (üå±)&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Fri Feb 10 18:12:07 +0000 2023&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/Fon-eRWWcAEhqP5.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/0J4FjfVeIe&quot;,&quot;alt_text&quot;:null}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:18,&quot;like_count&quot;:113,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{},&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1624108968686518285\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"tweet-link-top\"><div class=\"tweet-header\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/twitter_name/w_96/TheTreeverse.jpg\" alt=\"Twitter avatar for @TheTreeverse\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"tweet-header-avatar\"><div class=\"tweet-header-text\"><span class=\"tweet-author-name\">Treeverse (üå±) </span><span class=\"tweet-author-handle\">@TheTreeverse</span></div></div><div class=\"tweet-text\">You have $11 to build a team of tamed monsters.\n\nWho you picking? üëÄ </div><div class=\"tweet-photos-container one\"><div class=\"tweet-photo-wrapper \"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!D3bG!,w_600,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.substack.com%2Fmedia%2FFon-eRWWcAEhqP5.jpg\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!D3bG!,w_600,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.substack.com%2Fmedia%2FFon-eRWWcAEhqP5.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"tweet-photo\"></picture></div></div></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1624108968686518285\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"tweet-link-bottom\"><div class=\"tweet-footer\"><span class=\"tweet-date\">6:12 PM ‚àô Feb 10, 2023</span><hr><div class=\"tweet-ufi\"><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1624108968686518285/likes\" class=\"likes\"><span class=\"like-count\">113</span><span>Likes</span></span><span href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1624108968686518285/retweets\" class=\"retweets\"><span class=\"rt-count\">18</span><span>Retweets</span></span></div></div></a></div><p>As said in our previous monthly update. We are focusing on developing the IP of our character Baafi/Baafy. Here are a few more sneak peeks.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_58v!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb245ff53-454d-4d84-ada3-9488f85148af_1488x2266.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_58v!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.a